    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure is good according to their built every department have their seperate laboratories according to their subjects and specialization",
          "name": "Swaraj Bobade",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College canteen is another good thing also the garden where we can study in the shelter of trees",
          "name": "Shruti sahu",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Computer facilities are available anytime",
          "name": "Shruti sahu",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement officer and facilities both are good. If you study and work hard you can definitely achieve it.",
          "name": "Shruti sahu",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College fest are very big and enjoying.and enough.",
          "name": "Devashish Wankhade",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College placement is also good . And intership offer are good",
          "name": "Devashish Wankhade",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College campus is quite good. Facilities are good",
          "name": "Devashish Wankhade",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College is having 700+ tie-up companies for placement opportunities",
          "name": "Tanmay",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching was really good faculty supports everytime wherever we feel difficult to study",
          "name": "Tanmay",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College is having good parking space labs they also support for activities early functions and happen here building and overall campus looks good",
          "name": "Tanmay",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
